query:
UPDATE nodes
            SET location_uuid = $1, backup_configuration_uuid = $2, name = $3,
                description = $4, deployment_enabled = $5, maintenance_enabled = $6, public_url = $7,
                url = $8, sftp_host = $9, sftp_port = $10,
                memory = $11, disk = $12
            WHERE nodes.uuid = $13
